summary: Sandals. NiOverride heels. 17 items in chest. Currently for CBBE.
descriptionHtml:
[size=6]Description[/size]
[size=3]Mod was made for CBBE 3.4f
Items are in chest in Riverwood near river. Items are temperable, [size=6][size=3] armor stats like stats of daedric armor[/size][/size].
Color versions: black (gems: red, yellow, blue, purple, green), steel[size=3] (gems: red, blue, purple, green), [size=3]gold[size=3] (gems: red, blue, purple, green), [size=3][size=3][size=3]copper[size=3] (gems: red, blue, purple, green)
UNP version will be later... maybe

Mod requires NetImmerse Override for the heels. If you have RaceMenu you already have this. Otherwise you can get it separately here [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37481]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37481
[/url][/size][/size][/size][/size][/size][/size][/size][/size]

[size=3]Bikini (same style as sandals) is here (adult only) [size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/90158]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/90158
[/url][/size]
